extendedInfo.description: The leading executive event for the Middle East and international carrier community* 650+ senior representatives from the Middle East, Europe, Asia, Africa and North America* Over 220 companies represented* 40+ senior thought-leaders providing insight into carrier markets in the region* New venue: The Grand Hyatt Dubai with increased networking and meeting spaceConference Highlights:* Keynote panel discussion: investment strategies and diversifying wholesale service offerings* Strategic regional and international connectivity: co-operation, partnerships and new transit routes* Special focus: new developments in the Saudi Arabian telecommunications market* Content delivery: business models for the Middle East carrier market
